Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBWasteTransactionType

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBWasteTransactionType
public class JDBWasteTransactionType extends Object
The JDBWasteTransactionType class updates the table APP_WASTE_TRANSACTIONS. This table contains a single row for each unique Waste Transaction Type as stored in the APP_WASTE_TRANSACTIONS table.
